Text: Professional Services Agreement Cc Mr Nemec PCS has some proposed revisions to the Professional Services Agreement between Enron and PCS Would I need to forward these to your attention for review If so can you please advise what your fax number is and I will only fax the pages that have changes Thank you Kelly Fleuriot Project Consulting Services Inc Phone Fax

Professional Services Agreement Cc Mr Nemec Eric Romero faxed you comments and proposed revisions to the Professional Services Agreement between Enron and Project Consulting on and wanted to know if you have any comments on the revisions Mr Romero will be out of the office Wednesday and Thursday so please feel free to contact me with your comments and I will give the information to him upon his return Thank you Kelly Fleuriot Project Consulting Services Inc Phone Fax
